snippet.title: Bolf Early Access Trailer : Bowling + Golf = Bolf!
snippet.description:
Bolf, the game that is Golf and also Bowling, is coming to Steam Early Access on November 19, 2019. Visit the store page on Steam to wishlist Bolf: 

https://store.steampowered.com/app/1176970/Bolf/ 

http://www.simtenero.com/
